{"tid":2319533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持政府 支持聖誕新年攬炒商界] 聖誕新年兩星期所有市民留在家中 只可以派一人外出","createTime":"2020-12-10T07:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T07:16:26.000Z","uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0102c53f8813768cbd07538c8fc67112d67f152","tid":2319533,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"前香港立法會議員，前食物及衞生局政治助理的建制人士，應該代表政府，我哋一定支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得代老闆出糧比我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳凱欣在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，政府應該派出檢測車到有關屋苑，或者考慮派專人上樓，為居民檢測，並要求他們直到有結果後才離開。<br />\n<br />\n她又認為，第4波疫情的感染人數，病毒傳播力或感染後的病情，都比第三波嚴重，若政府繼續用第三波的應對方法，應對新一波疫情，只能起「止咳」作用。她建議政府應考慮利用本月20日至下月2日的14天，在每區設立檢測站，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">所有市民留在家中，只派一人外出買東西，因這段時間正正是冬至及聖誕等假期</span></strong></span>，不少市民都會選擇放長假，所以政府應該好好利用此時機，控制疫情，減少源頭不明個案數字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564540-20201210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564540-20201210.htm&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYphyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=cb19c4d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564540-20201210.htm&h=433f092c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564540-20201210.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8bf047488e3de16750ed87309f94a8e044a8fc0e","tid":2319533,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"酒店 食店 禮品店靠聖誕節新年追生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？大家一齊仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}